{start_of_bridge: Bridge}
[Gmaj7]     It was a long hot night
[Em7]She made it easy, she made it feel right
[Gmaj7]     But now it's over the moment has gone
I [F#7]followed my hands not my head, I know I was [Bm]wrong
{end_of_bridge}


